com.oneops.keywhiz

Class KeywhizClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oneops.keywhiz.KeywhizClient

  • public class KeywhizClient
extends Object
    Client for interacting with the Keywhiz Server.

    Facilitates the manipulation of Clients, Groups, Secrets and the connections between them.
